::Firearm::

Two ion disks hit Firearm's cannon, the Maximal transforming into robot mode. 
He flips through the air, landing perfectly on his feet. Growling at the fact 
that his arm cannon was damaged, Firearm spins to face Manterror, shooting a 
pistol and two optic lasers at the Pred.
